title: Swedish Buff Expansion - Europa Universalis IV mod
description:
Swedish Buff Expansion - Europa Universalis IV mod


Etract 7zip to your C:Users[user]Documents Paradox Interactive Europa Universalis IV mod folder


DESCRIPTION
With help from the Swedish government and a large group of top-notch Swedish 
scientists, Paradox Interactive is now able to bring the players of the wildy 
successful game Europa Universalis 4 back in time this mod which represents 
Sweden in a real and truthful light showing the true might of Sweden during this 
time period. With new historical records, Swedish historians have discovered that 
it was not Denmark who was the leader of the Kalmar Union, but it was Sweden. 
This mod, though in a conservative light, represents Sweden as the real power 
and innovator of the world. 

Although conservative, this mod buffs Sweden drastically. With its new and 
historical ideas, Sweden will be a powerhouse in EU4 thanks to the work of many 
historians and Paradox alike.
